      <title>英国贷款机构准备应对抵押贷款违约率再度上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-lenders-brace-for-fresh-increase-in-mortgage-defaults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于房主被迫以居高不下的借贷成本进行再融资，英国银行正准备迎接抵押贷款违约率的再次上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-lenders-brace-for-fresh-increase-in-mortgage-defaults</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:14:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lucid 首席执行官认为需要继续筹集资金以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/lucid-ceo-sees-need-to-continue-raising-money-for-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lucid 首席执行官 Peter Rawlinson 表示，公司的愿景是“成为电动汽车市场的主要参与者”，他讨论了与沙特阿拉伯公共投资基金的新合作伙伴关系以及与阿斯顿马丁的电动汽车技术许可协议。本周早些时候，该公司的季度产量和交付量均超出预期，这两个数字都比前三个月增长了 22%。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/lucid-ceo-sees-need-to-continue-raising-money-for-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利准备迎接价值 5.52 亿美元的商业地产热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/chile-commercial-real-estate-sales-to-put-552-million-in-property-on-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于智利两大房地产投资基金濒临清算，该国投资者正准备迎接罕见的大批商业建筑涌入市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/chile-commercial-real-estate-sales-to-put-552-million-in-property-on-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟 ESG 基金新规出台后，巴克莱面临 300 亿美元抛售风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/barclays-sees-30-billion-selloff-risk-amid-new-eu-esg-fund-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行分析师的研究显示，如果资产管理公司打算在新规下保留 ESG 标签，那么在欧洲提供 ESG 基金的基金管理公司可能需要出售近 300 亿美元的股票和债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/barclays-sees-30-billion-selloff-risk-amid-new-eu-esg-fund-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非天然气用户计划在 2026 年前确保天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/south-africa-gas-users-plan-venture-to-secure-supply-before-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非工业天然气用户正计划成立一家公司来确保供应，此前南非工业天然气唯一供应商表示将于 2026 年停止供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/south-africa-gas-users-plan-venture-to-secure-supply-before-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:43:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ING 的 Garvey 表示，条件“好得令人难以置信”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/conditions-too-good-to-be-true-says-ing-s-garvey-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ING 全球债务和利率策略主管 Padhraic Garvey 表示，目前市场正处于如此积极的环境组合中 - 没有大衰退或大公司违约，而且波动性极低 - 但他认为这可能好得令人难以置信，而且可能存在风险。他在彭博简报中与 Dani Burger 和 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/conditions-too-good-to-be-true-says-ing-s-garvey-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚再次降息，通胀率处于目标区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-cuts-rate-for-second-month-with-inflation-in-target-range</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着巴尔干国家的通胀持续下降，塞尔维亚央行连续数月第二次下调利率，并采取宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-cuts-rate-for-second-month-with-inflation-in-target-range</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司债券因 Ofwat 和标准普尔加大压力而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-bonds-dip-as-ofwat-s-p-crank-up-the-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国水务监管机构加强了对该公用事业公司的审查以及标准普尔全球评级表示可能将其评级下调为垃圾级之后，泰晤士水务公司的债券跌至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-bonds-dip-as-ofwat-s-p-crank-up-the-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息主题从美联储蔓延至中东欧，新兴市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于核心经济体和发展中经济体对货币宽松的押注不断增加，风险偏好保持强劲，新兴市场股市再创两年新高，货币上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>储备“武器化”是央行面临的最大风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/global-reserve-managers-worry-their-assets-are-at-risk-says-ubs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团的一项调查显示，各国央行储备经理越来越担心其货币资产的安全性，理由是全球地缘政治风险不断上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/global-reserve-managers-worry-their-assets-are-at-risk-says-ubs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
